<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/936665-if-you-re-a-student-of-abraham-lincoln">If you&#39;re a student of Abraham Lincoln already, what makes this particular book worth reading?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_936665'><a id="like_count_community_question_936665" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/936665?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F8753495-the-fiery-trial">like</a></span>

