<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/84193733-porter-broyles"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1547055349i/84193733._UX100_CR0,38,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/84193733-porter-broyles">Porter Broyles</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The book focuses on sources that were documented during his lifetime---if he uses a reference made after his lifetime, it highlights that fact. Much o<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The book focuses on sources that were documented during his lifetime---if he uses a reference made after his lifetime, it highlights that fact. Much of what we know includes stories recorded years or decades after his death.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
