<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/14894629-the-half-has-never-been-told"><img alt="The Half Has Never Been Told: Slavery and the Making of American Capitalism" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1390433357l/14894629._SX98_.jpg" />
