<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/44236.The_Civil_War_Vol_1"><img alt="The Civil War, Vol. 1: Fort Sumter to Perryville" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1345035610l/44236._SX98_.jpg" />
