<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/550931.Empire_of_Liberty"><img alt="Empire of Liberty: A History of the Early Republic, 1789-1815" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348976871l/550931._SX98_.jpg" />
